# Datasets Description

| Column Name | Data Type | Category | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| Patient ID | Object (String) | Categorical | Unique identification number assigned to each cancer patient. |
| Age | Integer | Numerical | Age of the patient in years. |
| Gender | Object | Categorical | Gender of the patient such as Male, Female, or Other. |
| Country Region | Object (String) | Categorical | Country or region where the patient belongs. |
| Year | Integer (int64) | Numerical | Year in which the patient record was captured (2015–2024). |
| Genetic Risk | Float | Numerical | Genetic predisposition score indicating inherited cancer risk level. |
| Air Pollution` | Float | Numerical | Air pollution exposure score affecting patient health condition. |
| Alcohol Use | Float | Numerical | Alcohol consumption level score of the patient. |
| Smoking | Float | Numerical | Smoking habit intensity/risk score. |
| Obesity Level` | Float  | Numerical | Obesity or body-fat-related risk score. |
| Cancer Type | Object (String) | Categorical | Type of cancer diagnosed (e.g., Lung, Breast, Skin, Leukemia, Colon). |
| Cancer Stage | Object (String) | Categorical | Stage of cancer progression (Stage 0, I, II, III, IV). |
| Treatment Cost USD | Float | Numerical | Estimated treatment expenditure in US Dollars. |
| Survival Years| Float | Numerical | Estimated survival duration after diagnosis in years. |
| Target-Severity Score | Float | Numerical (Target Variable) | Overall severity score representing cancer risk intensity and condition seriousness. |

